DevFest Nairobi 2024

A.S.K Dome, Jamuhuri, Nairobi, 00100

GDG Nairobi

DevFest Nairobi 2024: The ultimate tech event for developers in Nairobi. Join us for DevFest Nairobi 2024, learn from the industry's best, network with other developers, and build your skills. With tracks ranging from web development to mobile development to cloud and machine learning, there is something for everyone.

Oct 26, 5:00 AM – 2:00 PM (UTC)

﻿ RSVP'd

Key Themes

AIAndroidCloudDevFestFirebaseFlutter

About this event

DevFest Nairobi 2024 is a premier developer conference in Nairobi, Kenya. This one-day event brings together a vibrant community of developers, tech enthusiasts, and industry experts to explore the latest advancements in mobile, web, IoT, robotics, AI, and cloud technologies. Immerse yourself in inspiring talks, hands-on workshops, and networking opportunities as we shape the future of technology together.
